sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Mermaid Editor
    participant FS as File System
    participant Parser

    User->>App: File → Open (⌘O)
    App->>FS: open dialog
    FS-->>App: path + content
    App->>Parser: parse(source)
    Parser-->>App: DiagramModel

    loop auto-sync every 1.5 s
        App->>App: serialize(mutations)
        App-->>User: Monaco updates
    end

    alt valid diagram
        App-->>User: renders preview SVG
    else parse error
        App-->>User: shows error message in preview
    end

    Note right of User: ⌘↵ forces immediate sync
